VALUEPAIR.NAME: Command2
VALUEPAIR.VALUE:
cat $PMWorkflowLogDir/$PMWorkflowName_log.txt | tr -d '
' | sed 's/[[:digit:]]\{4\}-[[:digit:]]\{2\}-[[:digit:]]\{2\}/
/g' | grep 'ERROR' | grep -o '.\[.*.\]' | head -n 1| tr -d ']' | sed 's/\[/#!/bin/bash
session=/g' > $PMWorkflowLogDir/$PMWorkflowName_getlog.sh

VALUEPAIR.NAME: Command3
VALUEPAIR.VALUE:
echo "if [ -f $PMSessionLogDir/\$session.log.bin ] then /u01/Informatica/10.2.0/server/bin/infacmd.sh convertlogfile -in $PMSessionLogDir/\$session.log.bin -lo $PMSessionLogDir/\$session.log.txt cat $PMSessionLogDir/\$session.log.txt | tr '
' '\#' | sed 's/[[:digit:]]\{4\}-[[:digit:]]\{2\}-[[:digit:]]\{2\} /
/g' | grep '^ERROR' | head -n 1 | tr '\#' '
' > $PMSessionLogDir/$PMWorkflowName_Errorlog.txt elif echo \$session | grep -io 'get_ctrl_param' then echo 'ERROR Param_Value : $PMWorkflowName Parameter Value Failed from CTRL_JOB_PARAM_VAL' | sed 's/wf_//g; s/_INIT//g' > $PMSessionLogDir/$PMWorkflowName_Errorlog.txt elif echo \$session | grep -io 'wl_job' then echo 'ERROR Exec_Stus : $PMWorkflowName EXEC_STUS_LOG Failed' | sed 's/wf_//g; s/_INIT//g' > $PMSessionLogDir/$PMWorkflowName_Errorlog.txt elif echo \$session | grep -io 'get_table_cnt' then echo 'ERROR EXT_Table : $PMWorkflowName Table is EMPTY' | sed 's/wf_//g' > $PMSessionLogDir/$PMWorkflowName_Errorlog.txt else echo 'Undefined Error Please Check PWC_Monitor OR Contact Administrator' > $PMSessionLogDir/$PMWorkflowName_Errorlog.txt fi" >> $PMWorkflowLogDir/$PMWorkflowName_getlog.sh
